# Changelog

Русская версия: [CHANGELOG.ru.md](CHANGELOG.ru.md)

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/).

## [0.1.0] - 2026-06-16

### Added

- Initial public release of `hm-openrouter-monitoring`.
- Bilingual repository documentation in English and Russian.
- Manual installation, customization, and Hermes prompt guides.
- Public-safe Hermes skill documentation.
- Sanitized OpenRouter monitoring scripts.
- Example cron and JSON state files.
- Pytest-based tests for watchdog logic.
- GitHub Actions workflow for automated tests.